==Leaders==
The United National Party has had seven leaders since 1947. Ranil Wickremesinghe has been the leader of the party since 1994.

===Deputy leaders===
Below are a few notable deputy leaders of the party.
* Karu Jayasuriya (2008–2011)
* Sajith Premadasa (2011–2013)
* Karu Jayasuriya (2013–2014)
* Sajith Premadasa (2014–2019)
* Ruwan Wijewardene (2020–present)

